---
description: Prevent manual tenant scope handling
alwaysApply: true
---

In CephasOps runtime code:

Never manually use:

TenantScope.CurrentTenantId  
EnterPlatformBypass()  
ExitPlatformBypass()

Runtime services must always use:

TenantScopeExecutor.RunWithTenantScopeAsync(...)  
TenantScopeExecutor.RunWithPlatformBypassAsync(...)  
TenantScopeExecutor.RunWithTenantScopeOrBypassAsync(...)

Manual scope handling is allowed ONLY in:

DatabaseSeeder  
ApplicationDbContextFactory.CreateDbContext

Any new runtime service that manually sets tenant scope should be rejected.
